<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>They've been busy filming scenes for TOWIE's 10th anniversary special series in recent weeks, with the show airing later this month. </p>

<p>And Chloe Sims and Pete Wicks made the most of their downtime from work as they enjoyed a fun night out at Nightjar cocktail bar in London's Old Street on Wednesday night.</p>

<p>The reality starlet, 37, and her tattooed pal, 31, appeared in very high spirits as they left the bar at 1am before making their way down the street arm-in-arm.</p>

<p>Night out: Chloe Sims and Pete Wicks made the most of their downtime from TOWIE as they enjoyed a fun night out at Nightjar cocktail bar in London's Old Street on Wednesday night</p>

<p>The pair appeared to have had a great time as they flashed huge smiles as they walked, with a chivalrous Pete even carrying Chloe's black handbag. </p>

<p>Chloe and Pete dressed down for their cosy evening together, with Chloe donning a black leather jacket worn over a white top.</p>

<p>The beauty salon owner added a pair of pale blue ripped jeans and black boots to her look. </p>

<p>Her long blonde locks were left loose for the occasion, while she upped the glam with a sleek palette of make-up. </p>

<p>Fun times: The reality starlet, 37, and her tattooed pal, 31, appeared in high spirits as they left the bar at 1am before making their way down the street arm-in-arm</p>

<p>Pete meanwhile looked dapper in an all-black ensemble, consisting of a leather jacket, T-shirt, skinny jeans and pointed boots.</p>

<p>The Celebs Go Dating star finished off his look with a camel fedora hat. </p>

<p>The duo, who seemed slightly worse for wear, were seen leaving the hot spot in the early hours of the morning, while Chloe puffed away on a vape. </p>

<p>Last month, TOWIE released a trailer ahead of its special reunion episodes that air in September.</p>

<p>The best night: The pair appeared to have had a great time as they flashed huge smiles as they walked, with a chivalrous Pete even carrying Chloe's black handbag</p>

