<p>Other hilarious parts include Sam Faiers asking for a vajazzle and Gemma Collins telling people to 'Google her'.</p>

<p>TOWIE tweeted: 'SHUT UP! 10 years of #TOWIE!? BRAND NEW episodes coming this September, starting with an anniversary special.</p>

